title: For Sale:   Airforce Condor .25cal shrouded PCP air rifle ( complete package )
postcontent:
I am selling my custom 2012 Airforce Condor .25 caliber. This rifle has been fitted with an aftermarket shroud that reduces the sound of the shot dramatically. The round hitting it's target is usually louder than the actual shot. Don't let that fool you though. The Airforce Condor is the most powerful of all pellet guns that are either .177, .20,.22, and the mighty .25! An adjustable power wheel lets you control the velocity from 800-1200fps with 26 grain pellets. You get all the benefits of a silenced .22LR, but with the benefits of an airgun. This gun is absolutely devastating on small game out to 150 yards. The rifle uses a bottle of high pressure air that lasts about 40 shots before needing to be refilled back up to 3,000 psi. Don't worry, with this rifle comes with thousands of rounds of THE BEST pellets from a few different manufacturers. The prices of these guns run pretty high, but have lifetime warranties, and are built here in the USA. I will list everything that you will see in the pictures so you know exactly what you are buying. You will be all set and won't need a single upgrade other than your favorite scope. You will get a almost new pump and adapter to fill the rifle, and a lifetime supply of ammo to keep you shooting all day. I can sell the scope with the rifle, but expect to pay every penny I paid for it because high dollar scopes usually hold their value. ( Hawke Sidewinder Tac 30 6.5-20x42mm = $420 )
Everything you get in the package.
----------------------------------------------
Airforce Condor .25 PCP air rifle w/ 24" lothar walther barrel
Airforce folding bipod
Airforce 3600 psi 3 stage hand pump
R&L Airgun's custom shroud for maximum sound reduction
Phillips pellet holder
--------
450 Beeman Crow Magnum hollow point pellets ( 26 grain)
450 JSB Exact King domed pellets ( 25 grain )
450 JSB Predator Polymags ( 26 grain )
160 Eun Jin hunting pellets ( 35 grain )
80 Beeman quick cleaning pellets
---------
Scope is optional. It is the most envied scope of airgun users abroad. If you are familiar with the YouTube channel for EDGUNUSA, then you probably know what I mean.
If you want the scope, it comes with the adjustment wheel, cleaning cloth, rings, and hard case that it came in. Just specify in your reply if you'll be wanting the scope with the rifle.
Since the rifle has very little recoil, I have been using the Orion Steady Pix Deluxe camera mount, which allows me to set up a digital camera behind the scope to record my shots, hunts, ect. If You purchase the scope with the rifle, I'll include this mount for free. ( $50 value)
-----------
Price of package without scope and rings = $700
--------
Package with scope, rings, and camera mount = $1100
--------
I am not desperate to sell this gun. No low ball offers will be replied to. Price I have listed is VERY FAIR! These guns last forever, and are cheaper to shoot than even a .22LR. 
This is a serious air rifle, that gets 1" groups at 100 yards.
Would be able to travel for serious buyer, will not ship. Since this is an airgun, it is classified as a toy, thus allowing you to shoot practically anywhere as long as you don't damage property, or hit someone. These pellets go right through a 2x4 with ease, so always treat this gun as if you we're shooting a .22LR or any firearm for that matter.
This rifle is NOT back yard friendly without the shroud installed. The shroud is specifically made to attach to the frame of the rifle so as to not need special paperwork like an FFA silencer that would attach to the barrel of a firearm. Inside the shroud is 5 cone shaped plastic baffles that work in the same manner as the baffles in a silencer. In order to have full suppressed capability you don't need to buy a specific type of ammo, but rather adjust the power wheel on the rifle to drop the pellets below subsonic velocities. Feel free to email me if you are interested, or text me REDACTED and I can send you more pictures. I am willing to brief the buyer on how to operate the rifle and fill the rifle's high pressure air tank safely. I will also include the original box and instructions. I take care of all my guns extremely well, and will include the special gun oil that this rifle needs when you want to strip and clean the gun.
Text anytime. I am a creature of the night for sure and stay up late most of the time.
